  <description type="morphology">Plants 2.5–4 cm. Leaves of stipe and basal fronds in 3 or 11+ rows, 1–1.5 mm; dorsal frond leaves absent from stipe; distal stipe leaves asymmetric, 0.8–1 mm, margins serrate in distal 1/2; all leaves ovate; costa short or to 1/2–2/3 leaf length. Perichaetia with paraphyses present. Seta 1.5 cm, smooth. Capsule 1 mm; operculum long-rostrate, 1.5 mm.</description>
